# Oliver Kullmann, 15.4.2005 (Swansea)

-------------------------------------------

Necessary installations:

g++, version 3.4.3 or higher
(tested: 3.4.3, 3.4.4, 3.4.5, 4.0.0, 4.0.1, 4.0.2, 4.0.3, 4.1.0, 4.1.1)
(check: run "g++ -v")
Recommended: 4.1.1
Versions lower than 3.4.3 cannot compile the library
Problems:
 - 3.4.3 - 4.0.2, 4.1.0 fail for some foreign locales.
 - 3.4.3 - 4.0.2 do not detect all syntax errors (wrong handling
  of namespaces)
 - 3.4.6 cannot link the new test system, when optimisation is turned on
   (seems to be okay with 4.0.3 and later; unclear for the other versions).

Boost, version 1_33_1 or higher
(tested: 1_33_1)
Recommended: 1_33_1
BOOST = path to the source library
(for example BOOST = /usr/local/include/boost-1_33/)

GNU make, version 3.80 or higher
(check: run "make -v")

Doxygen, version 1.4.5 or higher (but not 1.4.6)
(tested: 1.4.5, 1.4.7)
(check: run doxygen --version)
Recommended: 1.4.7

Valgrind, version 3.1.0 or higher
Recommended: 3.2.0

----------------------------------------------

System requirements:

>= 512 MB main memory

